```python
# 获取文本向量
def test_text_encoder():
    import paddle
    from paddlenlp.experimental.semantic_search import Encoder
    # from paddlenlp.transformers.encoder import Encoder

    encoder = Encoder.from_pretrained("bert-base-uncased")
    input_ids = paddle.randint(100, 1000, [1, 10])
    features = encoder(input_ids)
    print(features.shape)

def test_text_encoder_with_embedding_type():
    import paddle
    from paddlenlp.experimental.semantic_search import Encoder


    encoder = Encoder.from_pretrained("bert-base-uncased", embedding_type='cls')
    input_ids = paddle.randint(100, 1000, [1, 10])
    features = encoder(input_ids)
    print(features.shape)


# 获取text-image的向量
def test_text_image_encoder():

    import paddle
    from paddlenlp.experimental.semantic_search import Encoder

    from PIL import Image
    import requests
    from paddlenlp.transformers import CLIPProcessor, CLIPVisionModel

    processor = CLIPProcessor.from_pretrained("openai/clip-vit-base-patch32")

    url = "http://images.cocodataset.org/val2017/000000039769.jpg"
    image = Image.open(requests.get(url, stream=True).raw)

    inputs = processor(images=image, return_tensors="pd")
    input_ids = paddle.randint(100, 1000, [1, 10])

    model = Encoder.from_pretrained("openai/clip-vit-base-patch32", embedding_type='cls')

    outputs = model.get_image_features(**inputs)
    outputs = model.get_text_features(input_ids)
    print(outputs.shape)
    print(outputs.shape)

    model = CLIPVisionModel.from_pretrained("openai/clip-vit-base-patch16")
```

title: Doccano标注数据迁移Label-studio
body:
### Feature request

在UIE微调文档中，以前推荐使用的是Doccano进行标注。最新文档推荐使用的是Label-studio标注工具，最终转换后的数据格式都是一样的。因此有一个需求是将使用Doccano标注的数据迁移如Label-studio标注工具中。
1. 标签转换
2. 标注数据转换

写了个简单的关系抽取的转换脚本
1.  标签导入
```
    def label_doccano2labelstudio(label_type, label_list):
        label_xml = ""
        for item in label_list:
            name, backgroundColor = item.get("text"), item.get("backgroundColor")
            if label_type == "entity":
                label_xml += f'<Label value="{name}" background="{backgroundColor}"/>'
            else:
                label_xml += f'<Relation value="{name}"/>\n'
        return label_xml
```

2. 标注数据转换
参考官方的labelstudio2doccano.py修改了一点点
```
  import argparse
  import os
  import json
  import random
  
  def random_idx():
      idx = ""
      for _ in range(10):
          num = random.randint(1, 58)
          while 26< num< 33:
              num = random.randint(1, 58)
          idx += chr(64+ num)
      return idx
  
  
  def append_attrs(data):
      '''
      将doccano中导出的数据转换为导入label-studio格式数据
      '''
      item, mapp = [], {}
  
      text = data["text"]
      for entity in data["entities"]:
          idd = entity["id"]
          
          id_doccano = random_idx()
          while id_doccano in mapp.values():
              id_doccano = random_idx
              
          label = entity["label"]
          start_offset = entity["start_offset"]
          end_offset = entity["end_offset"]
          
          item.append(
              {
                  'value': {'start': start_offset, 'end': end_offset, 'text': text[start_offset: end_offset], 'labels': [label]},
                  'id': f'{id_doccano}',
                  'from_name': 'label',
                  'to_name': 'text',
                  'type': 'labels',
                  'origin': 'manual'
              }
          )
          mapp[idd] = id_doccano
          
      for relation in data["relations"]:
          id  = relation["id"]
          from_id = relation["from_id"]
          to_id = relation["to_id"]
          type_doccano = relation["type"]
          
          item.append(
              {
                  'from_id': f'{mapp[from_id]}',
                   'to_id': f'{mapp[to_id]}',
                   'type': 'relation',
                   'direction': 'right',
                   'labels': [type_doccano]
              }
          )
          
      return item, text
  
  
  
  def convert(dataset):
      results = []
      outer_id = 0
      for data in dataset:
          item, text = append_attrs(data)
          results.append(
                          {
                              'id': outer_id,
                              'data': { 'text': f'{text}' },
                              'annotations': [{
                                              'id': outer_id,
                                              'result': item
                                              }]
                          }
                      )
              
      return results
  
  def do_convert(doccano_file, labelstudio_file):
  
      if not os.path.exists(doccano_file):
          raise ValueError("Please input the correct path of label studio file.")
  
      # 读取doccano标签数据
      with open(doccano_file, "r", encoding="utf-8") as f:
          dataset = []
          for line in f:
              dataset.append(json.loads(line.strip("\n")))
  
      # 写入labelstudio数据
      with open(labelstudio_file, "w", encoding="utf-8") as outfile:
          label_studio = convert(dataset)
          outfile.write(json.dumps(label_studio, ensure_ascii=False))
  
  
  if __name__ == "__main__":
      labelstudio_file = "{保存的路径及文件名.json}"
      doccano_file = "{通过Doccano标注工具导出的数据}"
      do_convert(doccano_file, labelstudio_file)
```

### Motivation

既然labelstudio2doccano.py 对labelstudio转换到doccano的脚本写了，希望能完善一下逆转的操作。
如果有人有这方面的需求就能减少别人不少的时间，感谢。

### Your contribution

```

        num = random.randint(1, 58)
        while 26< num< 33:

def append_attrs(data):
    '''
    将doccano中导出的数据转换为导入label-studio格式数据
    '''
    item, mapp = [], {}

    text = data["text"]
    for entity in data["entities"]:
        idd = entity["id"]

        while id_doccano in mapp.values():
            id_doccano = random_idx
            
        label = entity["label"]
        start_offset = entity["start_offset"]
        end_offset = entity["end_offset"]
        
        item.append(
            {
                'value': {'start': start_offset, 'end': end_offset, 'text': text[start_offset: end_offset], 'labels': [label]},
                'id': f'{id_doccano}',
                'from_name': 'label',
                'to_name': 'text',
                'type': 'labels',
                'origin': 'manual'
            }
        )
        mapp[idd] = id_doccano
        
    for relation in data["relations"]:
        id  = relation["id"]
        from_id = relation["from_id"]
        to_id = relation["to_id"]

        item.append(
            {
                'from_id': f'{mapp[from_id]}',
                 'to_id': f'{mapp[to_id]}',
                 'type': 'relation',
                 'direction': 'right',
                 'labels': [type_doccano]
            }
        )
        
    return item, text



def convert(dataset):
    results = []
    outer_id = 0
    for data in dataset:
        item, text = append_attrs(data)
        results.append(
                        {
                            'id': outer_id,
                            'data': { 'text': f'{text}' },

        outfile.write(json.dumps(label_studio, ensure_ascii=False))


if __name__ == "__main__":
    labelstudio_file = "{保存的路径及文件名.json}"
```
